{"tid":1649374,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港人自衛手冊","createTime":"2019-10-12T15:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T03:28:10.000Z","uid":121146,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"78ed0367c0996025e6a2491435d0605ef58372c1","tid":1649374,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:31:37.000Z","msg":"當你活在一個地方  <br />\n身上有兩張八達通卡 ＝ 有可疑<br />\n身穿黑衣 ＝ 有可疑<br />\n但全裸浮屍 ＝ 無可疑  的時候<br />\n人們不禁要問  這個政權  這個警隊  是否值得令你信任<br />\n<br />\n香港人要自衛  要互相幫助<br />\n我們要有體系  有邏輯  有原因<br />\n因此我嘗試歸納了以下幾個情況：<br />\n<br />\n1．被自稱便衣要求搜身時  應先要求出示委任證  <br />\n－ 如願意出示委任證  應先要求解釋合理懷疑之處  如不合理  市民有權繼續要求解釋<br />\n－ 如被拒絕  你可以提出一個合理時間（例如30秒）未能出示後  直接walk away<br />\n－ 如離開時被纏住  你可以要求在合理時間內縮手   否則使用武力  （如10秒）<br />\n注意：根據普通法  任何人只需要在合情合理  並且真誠地相信  對方在不合理情況下攻擊你  你就可以合法地自衛  前提是  使用對等武力<br />\n<br />\n2．無故被任何人士攻擊時  只要你當時並非襲擊任何人、並非被通輯<br />\n任何非對等之武力  皆被認為不恰當 （即使是警察）<br />\n在雷光火石之間  你所作出的任何反抗行為  均屬合法<br />\n<br />\n3．於街上有兄弟被捉時  市民有權要求出示委任證  <br />\n－ 如未能出示或自稱普通市民  你應即時要求在合理時間內解釋原因  如未能解釋  你將可以合法地救出被非法禁錮之兄弟<br />\n<br />\n4．有疑似警棒人士出現  而並沒有委任證時  你絕對有權反擊  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vicky.ng.54738/videos/397056347906360/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvicky.ng.54738%2Fvideos%2F397056347906360%2F&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9hR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=4d59c790\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/vicky.ng.54738/videos/397056347906360/</a><br />\n<br />\n記住  香港已經沒有所謂安全地方 <br />\n自己顧自己  下一個被打的  將會是你<br />\n唯有互相照顧  這裡才是安全地方<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論更多可能性  一齊努力"},{"pid":"a156e242c891a2b8219ec9d1efd11e179e63e664","tid":1649374,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2065f6093dee6633e7ebc56916b9c8be05b758c","tid":1649374,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f356228dde45bcc5055c5b4f07b9ba64148fe8d8","tid":1649374,"uid":149383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:37:29.000Z","msg":"屌 大家養成加密習慣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該加密嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就唔該加密啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好比班狗 同啲記者睇到<br />\n一陣又亂寫野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e0936d033a9eb85a325d673be23e8dfdd15c84","tid":1649374,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f356228dde45bcc5055c5b4f07b9ba64148fe8d8","tid":1649374,"uid":149383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:37:29.000Z","msg":"屌 大家養成加密習慣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該加密嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就唔該加密啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好比班狗 同啲記者睇到<br />\n一陣又亂寫野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"比班狗知道唔show委任證我地就會反擊都好  我地係時候set返條底線"},{"pid":"2afcfacc6037355e9815ed487ac54d97e90f54e6","tid":1649374,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:41:03.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c6df67782dcb4346230e7106e2eedbe582d6ca14","tid":1649374,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbbe9fafbc27efb0dabc90e6c3ebef48d85c4be3","tid":1649374,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/